Date: Wed, 8 Apr 2026 16:36:49 +0200
Subject: ipv6: move IFA_F_PERMANENT percpu allocation in process scope

From: Paolo Abeni <pabeni@redhat.com>

[ Upstream commit 8e6405f8218b3f412d36b772318e94d589513eba ]

